## 컨트롤러 작성 패턴

```java
@RestController
@RequiredArgsConstructor
@RequestMapping("/api/{리소스}")
public class SampleController {

    private final SampleService sampleService;

    @PostMapping
    public ResponseEntity<SampleResponse> create(
            @Valid @RequestBody SampleRequest request,
            @AuthenticationPrincipal CustomUserDetails user) {
        return ResponseEntity.ok(sampleService.create(request, user.getUsername()));
    }
}
```

- 현재 로그인 사용자: `@AuthenticationPrincipal CustomUserDetails user`
- 성공(생성): `ResponseEntity.created(URI).build()`
- 성공(조회/수정): `ResponseEntity.ok(data)`
- 성공(삭제): `ResponseEntity.ok().build()`
- 예외는 컨트롤러에서 try-catch 하지 않고 `GlobalExceptionHandler`에 위임

