## DTO 패턴

```java
// Request — Validation 어노테이션 필수
public class CreateSampleRequest {
    @NotBlank private String title;
    @NotNull  private Integer count;
}

// Response — record 타입 권장
public record SampleResponse(Long id, String title) {
    public SampleResponse(Sample entity) {
        this(entity.getId(), entity.getTitle());
    }
}
```

